<subSubSection id="C3776556EED73BB3FC9AFD47FBE4FC72" pageId="390" pageNumber="391" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BD236DDEED73BB3FC9AFD47FBE4FC72" blockId="390.[810,1452,275,947]" pageId="390" pageNumber="391">
<emphasis id="B919EACFEED73BB3FC9AFD47FC09FD62" bold="true" box="[863,972,649,675]" pageId="390" pageNumber="391">Remarks</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EEED73BB3FC24FD44FB9CFD62" authority="Kim &amp; Boxshall, 2020" authorityName="Kim &amp; Boxshall" authorityYear="2020" box="[993,1113,650,675]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Notopygus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="390" pageNumber="391" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B919EACFEED73BB3FC24FD44FB9CFD62" box="[993,1113,650,675]" italics="true" pageId="390" pageNumber="391">Notopygus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B919EACFEED73BB3FBA2FD47FB12FD62" bold="true" box="[1127,1239,649,675]" pageId="390" pageNumber="391">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4EED73BB3FBA2FD47FB12FD62" box="[1127,1239,649,675]" pageId="390" pageNumber="391" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
can be separated from the closely related genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EEED73BB3FB4FFD62FAC0FD04" authorityName="Thorell" authorityYear="1859" box="[1162,1285,684,709]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Doropygus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="390" pageNumber="391" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFEED73BB3FB4FFD62FAC0FD04" box="[1162,1285,684,709]" italics="true" pageId="390" pageNumber="391">Doropygus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by three main characters states: (1) one or more of the setal elements on the caudal ramus is transformed into a spine; (2) the metasome is swollen and bulbous; and (3) the third exopodal segment of leg 4 bears a total of 9 (rather than 8) armature elements. The last of these character states appears to be plesiomorphic relative to the state exhibited in 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EEED73BB3FC83FC54FC04FC72" authorityName="Thorell" authorityYear="1859" box="[838,961,922,947]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Doropygus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="390" pageNumber="391" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFEED73BB3FC83FC54FC04FC72" box="[838,961,922,947]" italics="true" pageId="390" pageNumber="391">Doropygus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
